    public abstract class DGAAbstractEdgeInputFormat<E extends Writable>
extends TextEdgeInputFormat<Text,E>
    Abstract class that simplifies the setup of our EdgeInputFormat subclasses. All DGA analytics require data to be specified in roughly the same way, while some algorithms may require a 3rd column with a weight and others may not care. The only duty of this class is to set up the edge reverse duplicator, and extract defaults or overrides from the GiraphConfiguration
